                "searchField": "crv.visruledradius tristan-huber visualize the radius of curvature on a ruled surface. threshold radius sets the point at which the heatmap is solid red. intended for testing if a surface is too tightly curved to manufacture abundance-tool",
                "owner": "tristan-huber",
                "description": "Visualize the radius of curvature on a ruled surface. Threshold radius sets the point at which the heatmap is solid red. Intended for testing if a surface is too tightly curved to manufacture",
                "contentURL": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tristan-huber/crv.VisRuledRadius/master/project.abundance?sanitize=true",
